# =========================================================================
#   NUCLEUS COACHING PLATFORM - RUNTIME ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# =========================================================================

# GEMINI_API_KEY: Required for premium AI Chatbot mentorship. 
# AI Studio automatically injects this at runtime from user secrets.
# Users can configure this via the Secrets panel in the AI Studio UI.
GEMINI_API_KEY="MY_GEMINI_API_KEY"

# APP_URL: The URL where this full-stack applet is hosted on Cloud Run.
# Used for responsive mobile relative protocol mappings and callbacks.
APP_URL="MY_APP_URL"

# SMTP_USER: Gmail or SMTP address used with Nodemailer SMTP (e.g., mail@gmail.com)
SMTP_USER=
# SMTP_PASS: Secure 16-character Google App Password (not your primary password)
SMTP_PASS=
# JWT_SECRET: Strong secret key used to sign and certify student session JWTs
JWT_SECRET=nucleus_cc_secret_auth_789!

# INTERST_PORT: Port on which the express server runs (Normally 3000)
PORT=3000


# =========================================================================
#   NUCLEUS COACHING PLATFORM - UNIFIED SYSTEM RECONSTRUCTION PROMPT
# =========================================================================
# 
# [INSTRUCTIONS FOR THE RECIPIENT AI BOT]:
# Please reproduce the Nucleus Coaching Platform, a high-fidelity, premium, full-stack 
# educational coaching platform led by IITians and Doctors. It features secure study 
# materials, reactive video courses, real-time OTP auth, dynamic SMTP sync, responsive 
# PWA systems, mobile compatibility (Capacitor), and server-side Gemini AI mentoring.
#
# Adhere strictly to the architectural specifications, file pathways, and visual guidelines
# specified below.
#
# =========================================================================
# 
# # ```markdown
# # # THE ULTIMATE NUCLEUS COACHING PLATFORM - MASTER SPECS
# # 
# # Build a fully functioning, professional-grade, full-stack educational coaching portal.
# # This app must support mobile compilation via Capacitor, and runs a server-side Express backend
# # coupled with a responsive React (TypeScript) frontend.
# # 
# # ## 1. MAIN STACK & LIBRARIES
# # Ensure the exact libraries are used for modern transitions, styling, and server interactions:
# # - **Frontend Framework**: React 19, TypeScript, Vite, HashRouter (React Router DOM v7).
# # - **Backend API**: Express server, Nodemailer for secure SMTP OTP verification, jsonwebtoken (JWT).
# # - **Database Backend**: Firebase SDK Client & Firestore Auth synchronization.
# # - **AI/GenAI engine**: Google GenAI (`@google/genai`) invoking 'gemini-3.5-flash'.
# # - **Animation & Scrolling**: Framer Motion (`motion/react`), Lenis smooth scrolling.
# # - **Styling Method**: Tailwind CSS with custom off-white ambient light theme in `src/index.css`.
# # - **Icons**: Lucide React (`lucide-react`).
# # 
# # ---
# # 
# # ## 2. DIRECTORY STRUCTURE
# # Replicate this exact folder structure:
# # - `/capacitor.config.ts` (Mobile core setup)
# # - `/server.ts` (Express gateway, Firestore Client SDK wrapper, nodemailer, JWT and Gemini API proxy)
# # - `/src/main.tsx` (App mounting, native-mobile fetch intercepts, custom proxy mappings)
# # - `/src/App.tsx` (Lenis initialization, routing, authentication syncing, global themes)
# # - `/src/index.css` (Tailwind root and glassmorphic parameters)
# # - `/src/lib/apiGateway.ts` (Structured Database API proxy service with live performance telemetry logs)
# # - `/src/lib/firebase.ts` (Standard clients and custom error hooks)
# # - `/src/store/` (zustand states: authStore.ts, contentStore.ts, settingsStore.ts)
# # - `/src/components/`
# #   * Navbar.tsx (Responsive blur-dock navigation header)
# #   * Footer.tsx (Modern interactive platform links grid)
# #   * LiquidGlassDock.tsx (Aesthetic floating dock with hover bubble scale transitions)
# #   * AIAssistantBot.tsx (Double interface: miniature float dock, extensive sidebar, live typing states)
# #   * SecurePdfViewer.tsx (Canvas-based watermarked lockable study document component)
# #   * CustomVideoPlayer.tsx (Secure overlay player blocking screenshots/context menu, displaying real-time email watermark)
# #   * ScreenProtector.tsx (Keyboard and printscreen listener triggers and reports breaches to Firestore)
# # - `/src/pages/`
# #   * Home.tsx (IIT/Doctor faculties marquee, QR registers, course cards, dynamic parallax bg blobs)
# #   * Login.tsx & Signup.tsx (SMTP OTP trigger views with beautiful transitions)
# #   * VerifyOtp.tsx & ForgotPassword.tsx (JWT certified codes password updates)
# #   * Dashboard.tsx (Interactive calendar timelines, streak systems, syllabus grids)
# #   * SelectStandard.tsx (Curriculum tier selection screens)
# #   * Learn.tsx (Course checklists, secure document PDFs & video play layouts)
# #   * Library.tsx (Dynamic resource indexes)
# #   * AdminDashboard.tsx (Unified administrative center: SMTP syncer, active devices table, chatbot telemetry dashboards, global materials modifiers)
# # 
# # ---
# # 
# # ## 3. CORE FILE SPECS & IMPLEMENTATION LOGIC
# # 
# # ### A. MOBILE ADAPTORS & SYSTEM PORTS
# # - **`/capacitor.config.ts`**:
# #   ```ts
# #   import { CapacitorConfig } from '@capacitor/cli';
# #   const config: CapacitorConfig = {
# #     appId: 'com.nucleus.coaching',
# #     appName: 'Nucleus Coaching Platform',
# #     webDir: 'dist',
# #     server: { androidScheme: 'https' }
# #   };
# #   export default config;
# #   ```
# # - **`/src/main.tsx`**:
# #   Must intercept client `window.fetch` requests dynamically. If running on native mobile device contexts (Capacitor or localhost), prepend relative `/api/*` endpoints with the live Cloud Run deployment server URL so that API communications remain unbroken.
# # 
# # ### B. UNIFIED Express Backend (`/server.ts`)
# # - **FirestoreWrapper**: Creates a clean backend wrapping class for the Firebase Client SDK to mimic native server SDK structures seamlessly without requiring heavy private credentials files.
# # - **Secure Bot Configurations**: Looks for `secure_bot.json`, falls back to `process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY`, and falls back to firestore `settings/secure_bot` to initialize `GoogleGenAI` cleanly.
# # - **Dynamic SMTP Email OTP Authentication**:
# #   Hosts dynamic server configuration `smtp_config` document inside firestore. When administrators synchronize secure SMTP variables on the dashboard, the backend recreates the active Nodemailer transporter globally instantly.
# # - **API Endpoints**:
# #   - `POST /api/auth/send-otp`: Sends mathematical 6-digit OTP verification codes via SMTP with fallback cache maps if offline.
# #   - `POST /api/auth/verify-otp`: Confirms validity, certified with high-security JWT access tokens.
# #   - `POST /api/auth/register` & `/api/auth/login-otp`: Registers/authenticates students on database based on verified JWT session claims.
# #   - `POST /api/chatbot/chat`: Feeds student text history into Gemini, including context structures about the student syllabus, performance latency indicators, and saves logs into database.
# #   - `GET /api/chatbot/logs`: Fetches chatbot requests list for administrative diagnostic monitors.
# # 
# # ### C. FRONTEND TELEMETRY API GATEWAY (`/src/lib/apiGateway.ts`)
# # Creates a single singleton Class broker (`apiGateway`) wrapping CRUD operations for users, materials, settings, active devices, and security violations.
# # - Implements strict latency timing audit hooks on database callbacks using `performance.now()`.
# # - Captures active sliding-window lists of the last 50 transactions, with live diagnostic callbacks allowing real-time telemetry graphs on the administrator dashboard.
# # - Reports screenshot/printscreen violation events to sub-collections securely upon device listener events.
# # 
# # ### D. PREMIUM INTERACTION COMPONENTS
# # - **`AIAssistantBot.tsx`**:
# #   Integrates a beautiful dual chat client (floating dock interface that expands to a spacious chat panel). Features custom suggestions, real-time response streams, current latency telemetry, and automatic content suggestions depending on the active student page directory.
# # - **`SecurePdfViewer.tsx`**:
# #   Renders study documents defensively. Disables copy selection, blocks right-click context menu events, overlays dynamic watermarks displaying the authenticated student's email and IP directly on materials, and blocks traditional keyboard printscreen combinations.
# # - **`CustomVideoPlayer.tsx`**:
# #   Provides HTML5 styled controls with dynamic canvas-based translucent student email panels tracking across the playback window periodically to prevent unauthorized external camera recording.
# # 
# # ### E. RICH STUDENT & WORKSPACE INTERFACES
# # - **`Home.tsx`**:
# #   Build and bundle high-concept design assets. Includes infinite scrolling horizontal lists of IIT/Doctor faculties, floating animated course modules, detailed course pricing calculators, responsive download badges, and custom seasonal overlay blobs matching scroll velocity patterns.
# # - **`AdminDashboard.tsx`**:
# #   The ultimate platform command deck. Integrates:
# #   1. Live SMTP credentials configuration syncer.
# #   2. Active multi-device login lists with remote-kill toggle switches.
# #   3. Real-time API telemetry audit logger demonstrating transaction millisecond latencies on a high-fidelity diagnostic panel.
# #   4. Global chatbot parameters setting page (Gemini context customizer).
# #   5. Complete materials administrator controls (adding, modifying, or deleting secured PDFs/videos).
# # - **`Learn.tsx`**:
# #   Interactive course syllabus lists. Allows students to track lecture videos, complete course units, toggle checklist statuses, view materials in side-by-side split screen containers, and interact with the tutor chatbot contextually.
# # 
# # *(Build full-fidelity files with no features mocked out; write clean TypeScript, and use beautiful Tailwind CSS styling variables targeting the Inter sans and JetBrains Mono monospace typography).*
# # ```
